SSL:
sudo apt install certbot
sudo certbot certonly --nginx -d dorantech.ir -d www.dorantech.ir
Generate certificate by TXT DNS instead of port80
sudo certbot -d dorantech.ir -d www.dorantech.ir --manual --preferred-challenges dns-01 certonly
